The teacher gives a task in the lesson:
- Children, come up with the beginning of the sentence so that the phrase "As I actually expected!" comes up as a continuation!
Vitya:
- Dad went on a business trip, and brought me a gift...
Petya:
- In the evening I baited a place in the pond, and in the morning I caught a lot of fish there...
Vovochka:
- Katka Puzyreva from the parallel class does an excellent m%no...
